snippet.description:

From the director of Prey, watch the brand-new trailer for Predator: Badlands, in theaters November 7.

The film is directed by Dan Trachtenberg and produced by John Davis, Dan Trachtenberg, Marc Toberoff, Ben Rosenblatt, Brent O’Connor.

snippet.title: Brittany Force makes the fastest run in NHRA history
snippet.description:
The first matchup of 340-plus-mph dragsters didn't disappoint as Brittany Force not only defeated Doug Kalitta but did it with the fastest speed ever, a national-record 341.85 mph on a 3.659 pass. Her run is quicker than her Funny Car teammate Austin Prock's 341.68 from last year's season finale. This event has now been host to four of the six fastest speeds in Top Fuel history.
